{"data":[{"date":"10:27 13/07","title":"Ivan Perisic ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Croatia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/ivan-perisic-tiet-lo-ly-do-giup-croatia-co-the-danh-bai-phap.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ivan Perisic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Inter Milan ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Les Bleus trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Croatia l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCroatia kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao \u1edf World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao. Luka Modric t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina 3-0 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ivan Perisic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ivan Perisic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/Ivan-Perisic-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Phap-vs-Croatia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T Croatia l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Dalic d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u0169ng g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D, b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Argentina. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, Croatia \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee1 v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u c\u00e2n n\u00e3o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Anh, Croatia th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 5. Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 kinh nghi\u1ec7m gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00fa ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 sau 120 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-croatia-vs-anh-421-190986.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Croatia vs Anh </span>gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Ph\u00e1p \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ec9 kho\u1ea3ng 4 tri\u1ec7u d\u00e2n nh\u01b0 Croatia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Perisic ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c gi\u00fap Croatia \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Perisic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Inter Milan ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Les Bleus trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Perisic\" title=\"Perisic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/mourinho-tiet-lo-ly-do-muon-dua-perisic-ve-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Perisic quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m b\u00e1o th\u00f9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u0103m 1998, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thua Ph\u00e1p 1-2 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Croatia b\u00e2y gi\u1edd v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t cay \u0111\u1eafng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng b\u00e1o th\u00f9. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n mang l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui cho NHM\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 th\u00eam 3 gi\u1edd, 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua. Tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Croatia, t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Croatia l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1212","checkdouble":"191086"},{"date":"10:05 13/07","title":"H\u00e9 l\u1ed9 c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 hai ph\u1ea3i chia tay M.U trong 48 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/14/he-lo-cai-ten-thu-hai-phai-chia-tay-mu-trong-48-gio-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 hai s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chia tay CLB Man Utd trong v\u00f2ng 48 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \">M.U chia tay&nbsp;Daley Blind</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Daley Blind\" title=\"Daley Blind\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/15/ajax-chi-mua-lai-daley-blind-voi-mot-dieu-kien.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>M.U chia tay Daley Blind trong 48 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao b\u1ecb th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng t\u1ea1i M.U d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Mourinho khi lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 y\u1ebfu \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 sau nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Chris Smalling, Phil Jones, Eric Bailly v\u00e0 Victor Lindelof, ng\u00e0y chia tay M.U c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Daley Blind \u0111ang t\u1edbi r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 19 tu\u1ed5i Diogo Dalot t\u1eeb Porto.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Mirror d\u1eabn ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb De Telegraaf c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Lan x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn, Daley Blind \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Ajax v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t trong v\u00f2ng 48 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Blind kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford khi ch\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00fang 7 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i Premier League. V\u00ec l\u00fd do \u0111\u00f3 anh \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i v\u00e0 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Ajax. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Ajax r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Blind tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i H\u00e0 Lan s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1edfi h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Champions League s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 25/7 t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t trong 48 ti\u1ebfng t\u1edbi, Daley Blind s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 2 \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i 1 chia tay Man United trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc anh,&nbsp;th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Sam Johnstone \u0111\u00e3&nbsp;chia tay M.U \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o West Brom v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/mu-day-manh-qua-trinh-mua-gareth-bale-180-191077.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/1/gareth-bale-duoc-khuyen-bo-real-ve-voi-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/mu-day-manh-qua-trinh-mua-gareth-bale-180-191077.html\">M.U \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 &ldquo;sao b\u1ef1&rdquo; Real</span><br>\r\nSau khi m\u1ea5t \u0111i Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0o tay Juventus, Real Madrid l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi n\u1ed7i lo m\u1ea5t th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao n\u1eefa. Th\u00f4ng tin MU \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh mua Gareth...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-127-mu-theo-duoi-1-chang-cristiano-khac-cua-sporting-184-191057.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-127-mu-theo-duoi-1-chang-cristiano-khac-cua-sporting.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-127-mu-theo-duoi-1-chang-cristiano-khac-cua-sporting-184-191057.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 12/7: MU theo \u0111u\u1ed5i 1 ch\u00e0ng Cristiano kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Sporting</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 12/7.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-tiet-lo-ly-do-muon-dua-perisic-ve-mu-172-191059.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/mourinho-tiet-lo-ly-do-muon-dua-perisic-ve-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-tiet-lo-ly-do-muon-dua-perisic-ve-mu-172-191059.html\">Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau MU sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Anh</span><br>\r\nHLV Jose Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ivan Perisic t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford sau khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ghi b\u00e0n khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u00f4m h\u1eadn.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1211","checkdouble":"191087"},{"date":"10:17 13/07","title":"Sao Roma kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Ronaldo c\u1ee7a Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/kevin-strootman-khong-ngai-doi-dau-ronaldo-tai-serie-a.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Cesc Fabregas cho r\u1eb1ng ch\u00ednh th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn anh \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-137-conte-da-bi-chelsea-sa-thai-421-191062.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte</span> ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm mu\u1ed9n b\u1edfi tin t\u1ee9c n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n b\u00e1o uy t\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn. V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i ngay c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Cesc Fabregas \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u00ec ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec nghi ng\u1edd n\u1eefa.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte, Fabregas t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 tr\u00e1ch c\u1ee9 th\u1ea7y c\u0169 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte, Fabregas t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 tr\u00e1ch c\u1ee9 th\u1ea7y c\u0169 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/tu-biet-conte-sao-chelsea-khong-quen-trach-moc-mot-chuyen.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Fabregas l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau khi Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 31 tu\u1ed5i tr\u00ean trang Twitter c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n: \u201cC\u1ea3m \u01a1n th\u1ea7y v\u00ec nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u Premier League v\u00e0 FA Cup. Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng g\u00ec cho t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n trong m\u1eaft th\u1ea7y nh\u01b0ng sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o. Ch\u00fac th\u1ea7y m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e2y, Fabregas c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u00fd tr\u00e1ch c\u1ee9 Conte kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng anh trong m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf World Cup 2018. C\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Arsenal n\u00f3i th\u00eam:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng khi Conte m\u1edbi l\u00ean n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n \u1edf Chelsea, c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 t\u00f4i m\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i nh\u00e0 \u1edf World Cup 2018, khi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1ee9a U19 v\u00e0 U21 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng h\u01a1n. Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u00ec h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t trong su\u1ed1t hai n\u0103m qua.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1eeb bi\u1ec7t Conte, Fabregas chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ef1u HLV Maurizio Sarri c\u1ee7a Napoli.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-chuong-su-moi-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang-172-187380.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-thu-thach-long-kien-nhan-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-chuong-su-moi-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang-172-187380.html\">Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri: Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1eed m\u1edbi v\u1edbi g\u00e3 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng</span><br>\r\nChelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri thay th\u1ebf HLV Conte trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao v\u00e0 qua \u0111\u00e2y, Stamford Bridge s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i, k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1210","checkdouble":"191088"},{"date":"10:53 13/07","title":"MU ch\u1ed1t 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 tuy\u1ec3n Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/mu-chot-50-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-tuyen-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho mu\u1ed1n MU mua Maguire</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede World Cup 2018, Harry Maguire l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 m\u00e0 anh c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u1edf kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/mu-chot-50-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-tuyen-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Maguire g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi 1 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 5 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf World Cup 2018. Phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh khi\u1ebfn Mourinho \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMU mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester, HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Maguire c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Leicester, anh ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ee7 38 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, ghi 2 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 4 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. C\u1ea7u&nbsp;th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/man-city-chi-50-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-cua-leicester-172-177232.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man City c\u0169ng h\u1ecfi mua Maguire </span>song Leicester \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 bu\u1ed9c h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Lapore c\u1ee7a Bilbao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>MU ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Maguire</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Leicester b\u00e1n Maguire, MU ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n King Power kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh l\u00ean 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Maguire\" title=\"Harry Maguire\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Anh-vao-ban-ket-World-Cup-Lai-la-nguoi-hung-Harry,-nhung-khong-phai-nhu-ban-dang-nghi!-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Harry Maguire</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLeicester ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Maguire, n\u1ebfu b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i cho MU v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e3i l\u1edbn trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean,&nbsp;&ldquo;B\u1ea7y c\u00e1o&rdquo; s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 bu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ph\u1ea3i chi th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan City \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mahrez, h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i chi t\u1edbi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i. M.U nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Maguire \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i, Mourinho s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7. V\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh Maguire s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1209","checkdouble":"191089"},{"date":"11:56 13/07","title":"Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: \u0110\u00e3 r\u00f5 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/chung-ket-world-cup-2018-xac-dinh-trong-tai-bat-chinh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, danh t\u00ednh tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn vinh d\u1ef1 c\u1ea7m c\u00f2i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina, Nestor Pitana.</h2><h2>X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/Chung-ket-World-Cup-2018-Xac-dinh-trong-tai-bat-chinh--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Nestor Pitana \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5\u00a0b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 22h00 t\u1ed1i Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i gi\u1eefa m\u1ed9t b\u00ean l\u00e0 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd cho ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u00ean l\u00e0 \u0110T Croatia \u0111ang l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd b\u00f3ng l\u0103n, danh t\u00ednh v\u1ecb vua \u00e1o \u0111en s\u1ebd \u2018c\u1ea7m c\u00e2n, n\u1ea3y m\u1ef1c\u2019 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u quan tr\u1ecdng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina, Nestor Pitana.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Pitana kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean qu\u00e1 xa l\u1ea1 t\u1ea1i World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y khi t\u1eebng b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Uruguay. D\u00f9 b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd (khi Argentina v\u1eeba b\u1ecb Ph\u00e1p lo\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8) nh\u01b0ng \u201c\u00f4ng vua \u00e1o \u0111en\u201d n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f4ng t\u00e2m trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, v\u1ecb vua \u00e1o \u0111en n\u00e0y c\u00f2n l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Croatia v\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng gi\u1eefa Nga - Saudi Arabia v\u00e0 Mexico - Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Nestor Pitana nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a FIFA \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7m c\u00f2i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. Hai tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Pitana s\u1ebd l\u00e0 hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Hernan Maidana v\u00e0 Juan Belatti.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:\n16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ivan-perisic-tiet-lo-ly-do-giup-croatia-co-the-danh-bai-phap-421-191086.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/ivan-perisic-tiet-lo-ly-do-giup-croatia-co-the-danh-bai-phap.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ivan-perisic-tiet-lo-ly-do-giup-croatia-co-the-danh-bai-phap-421-191086.html\">Ivan Perisic ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Croatia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p</span><br>\r\nIvan Perisic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Croatia, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Inter Milan ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Les Bleus trong tr\u1eadn chung...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/pogba-khong-dam-coi-thuong-croatia-421-191079.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/pogba-khong-dam-coi-thuong-croatia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/pogba-khong-dam-coi-thuong-croatia-421-191079.html\">Pogba n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Chung k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p \u0110T Croatia?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Croatia.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-thuc-chien-dich-world-cup-harry-kane-tran-tre-hy-vong-vao-tuong-lai-421-191067.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/ket-thuc-chien-dich-world-cup-harry-kane-tran-tre-hy-vong-vao-tuong-lai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-thuc-chien-dich-world-cup-harry-kane-tran-tre-hy-vong-vao-tuong-lai-421-191067.html\">K\u1ebft th\u00fac chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup, Harry Kane tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec1 ra, nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane tin t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0110T Anh s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</span></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1208","checkdouble":"191090"},{"date":"10:53 13/07","title":"T\u1eeb bi\u1ec7t Conte, sao Chelsea kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean tr\u00e1ch m\u00f3c m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ec7n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/tu-biet-conte-sao-chelsea-khong-quen-trach-moc-mot-chuyen.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Cesc Fabregas cho r\u1eb1ng ch\u00ednh th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn anh \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-137-conte-da-bi-chelsea-sa-thai-421-191062.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte</span> ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm mu\u1ed9n b\u1edfi tin t\u1ee9c n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n b\u00e1o uy t\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn. V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i ngay c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Cesc Fabregas \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u00ec ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n g\u00ec nghi ng\u1edd n\u1eefa.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte, Fabregas t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 tr\u00e1ch c\u1ee9 th\u1ea7y c\u0169 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte, Fabregas t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 tr\u00e1ch c\u1ee9 th\u1ea7y c\u0169 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/tu-biet-conte-sao-chelsea-khong-quen-trach-moc-mot-chuyen.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Fabregas l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau khi Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 31 tu\u1ed5i tr\u00ean trang Twitter c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n: \u201cC\u1ea3m \u01a1n th\u1ea7y v\u00ec nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u Premier League v\u00e0 FA Cup. Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng g\u00ec cho t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n trong m\u1eaft th\u1ea7y nh\u01b0ng sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o. Ch\u00fac th\u1ea7y m\u1ecdi s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e2y, Fabregas c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u00fd tr\u00e1ch c\u1ee9 Conte kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng anh trong m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf World Cup 2018. C\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Arsenal n\u00f3i th\u00eam:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng khi Conte m\u1edbi l\u00ean n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n \u1edf Chelsea, c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 t\u00f4i m\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i nh\u00e0 \u1edf World Cup 2018, khi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1ee9a U19 v\u00e0 U21 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng h\u01a1n. Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 th\u00ec h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t trong su\u1ed1t hai n\u0103m qua.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1eeb bi\u1ec7t Conte, Fabregas chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ef1u HLV Maurizio Sarri c\u1ee7a Napoli.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-chuong-su-moi-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang-172-187380.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-thu-thach-long-kien-nhan-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-chuong-su-moi-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang-172-187380.html\">Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri: Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1eed m\u1edbi v\u1edbi g\u00e3 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng</span><br>\r\nChelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri thay th\u1ebf HLV Conte trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao v\u00e0 qua \u0111\u00e2y, Stamford Bridge s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i, k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1207","checkdouble":"191091"},{"date":"11:20 13/07","title":"Emery l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u01b0\u1edbc b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/24/emery-len-ke-hoach-tuoc-bang-doi-truong-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha mong mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t Arsenal lu\u00f4n thi\u1ebfu t\u01b0 ch\u1ea5t l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o, th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n nh\u01b0ng trung v\u1ec7 Laurent Koscielny c\u00f3 l\u1ebd v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng ng\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng y\u00ean sau chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi. HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Arsenal:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Arsenal thi\u1ebfu ch\u1ea5t l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Arsenal thi\u1ebfu ch\u1ea5t l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/emery-len-ke-hoach-tuoc-bang-doi-truong-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao l\u00e2u v\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 n\u0103m, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i th\u00ec t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ai.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cKoscielny l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u00ecm th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi c\u00e1 t\u00ednh ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n m\u1ed9t Arsenal t\u1ef1 tin, c\u00e1 t\u00ednh v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cao h\u01a1n trong m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp n\u1eefa.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e2y, Emery c\u0169ng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 v\u1edbi n\u0103m t\u00e2n binh Lucas Torreira, Bernd Leno, Matteo Guendouzi, Stephan Lichtsteiner v\u00e0 Sokratis Papastathopoulos. T\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft su\u00f4n s\u1ebb tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng v\u1edbi chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a \u201cqu\u00e2n xanh\u201d Boreham Wood trong ng\u00e0y mai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau \u0111\u00f3, Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd tham gia gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu th\u01b0\u1eddng ni\u00ean ICC v\u1edbi ba tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t g\u1eb7p Atletico Madrid, Paris Saint-Germain v\u00e0 Chelsea, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Emirates ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Sevilla, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh Emery d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u0103ng quang v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League \u0111\u1ebfn ba l\u1ea7n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-bo-nhiem-emery-van-de-la-can-luc-nay-khong-phai-la-muon-ve-sau-172-186941.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/24/arsenal-bo-nhiem-emery-van-de-la-can-luc-nay-khong-phai-la-muon-ve-sau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-bo-nhiem-emery-van-de-la-can-luc-nay-khong-phai-la-muon-ve-sau-172-186941.html\">Arsenal b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Emery: V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7n l\u00fac n\u00e0y, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n v\u1ec1 sau\u2026</span><br>\r\nH\u00e0nh trang 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p, v\u1ecb HLV x\u1ee9 Basque v\u1eabn c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Emirates ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng s\u1ef1 ho\u00e0i nghi m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1206","checkdouble":"191092"},{"date":"10:56 13/07","title":"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Sarri quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Chelsea \u201cph\u1ee5 t\u00ecnh\u201d Conte?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/goc-nhin-chelsea-quyet-dinh-thay-the-conte-bang-sarri.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh, Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay th\u1ebf Conte b\u1eb1ng Sarri. H\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng cho Conte \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea \u201cph\u1ea3n b\u1ed9i\u201d Conte</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Antonio Conte t\u1ea1i Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb n\u00e9m v\u00e0o gi\u00f4ng b\u00e3o sau khi h\u1ecd tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd. K\u1ebft th\u00fac chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch Premier League, The Blues ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 5 tr\u00ean BXH, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u0169ng ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Conte th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 Alvaro Morata, Tiemoue Bakayoko, Danny Drinkwater hay Davide Zappacosta\u2026 C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam c\u00e1 t\u00ednh m\u1ea1nh khi\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng t\u1ea1i Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay th\u1ebf Conte b\u1eb1ng Sarri G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay th\u1ebf Conte b\u1eb1ng Sarri G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/goc-nhin-chelsea-quyet-dinh-thay-the-conte-bang-sarri.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay th\u1ebf Conte b\u1eb1ng Sarri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1eb3ng th\u1ebf m\u00e0 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Chelsea ngang nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng HLV kh\u00e1c b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p tr\u00ean danh ngh\u0129a Conte v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u1ed3i gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng. D\u01b0\u1edbi g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn c\u1ee7a Conte, \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec m\u1ed9t b\u00e0 v\u1ee3 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea3n b\u1ed9i ngay c\u1ea3 khi ch\u01b0a ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ly h\u00f4n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u1edd b\u00e1o uy t\u00edn c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i Conte, ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. S\u00e1ng h\u00f4m qua, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 48 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Chelsea t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng, song sau khi b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 th\u00f4ng tin, h\u1ecd d\u1eebng t\u1eadp v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i chi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Conte lo so se bi sa thai\" title=\"Conte lo s\u1ee3 s\u1ebd b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/19/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-137-Conte-da-bi-Chelsea-sa-thai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Conte ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 sa th\u1ea3i Conte</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, trong nay mai, danh t\u00ednh t\u00e2n HLV Chelsea s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ai kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i Maurizio Sarri. \u0110\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Conte \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Napoli c\u00e1ch ch\u1ee9c sau m\u00f9a 2017/18 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Carlo Ancelotti. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1eb1ng Conte s\u1ebd s\u1edbm b\u1ecb Chelsea d\u1ee9t t\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng Jorginho c\u1ee7a Sarri t\u1ea1i Napoli l\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eaft g\u1eb7p chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb sang Anh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea. M\u1ed9t khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 26 tu\u1ed5i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Man City t\u1edbi Chelsea, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00ec ti\u1ec1n. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 vi\u1ec7c Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay th\u1ebf Conte b\u1eb1ng Sarri m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y Jorginho \u201cl\u1eadt k\u00e8o\u201d v\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-sao-khung-serie-a-bay-sang-anh-ky-hop-dong-voi-dai-gia-premier-league-172-190983.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/30/cuc-nong-sao-khung-serie-a-bay-sang-anh-ky-hop-dong-voi-dai-gia-premier-league.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-sao-khung-serie-a-bay-sang-anh-ky-hop-dong-voi-dai-gia-premier-league-172-190983.html\">C\u1ef1c n\u00f3ng: Sao kh\u1ee7ng Serie A bay sang Anh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i gia Premier League</span><br>\r\n<span>Jorginho c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Premier League l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra trong 24h t\u1edbi, theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n bay \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1edbi Anh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sarri quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNapoli thay Sarri sau m\u00f9a 2017/18 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n n\u1eb1m \u1edf chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mi\u1ec1n Nam Italia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch th\u1ee9 2 t\u1ea1i Serie A, gi\u00e0nh 91 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u2013 con s\u1ed1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed CLB v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m so v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t Juventus c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay t\u1eeb khi Serie A m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u01b0a kh\u1edfi tranh, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Juventus d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Napoli d\u1ea1t d\u00e0o n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Sarri m\u1edbi khi\u1ebfn cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gay c\u1ea5n t\u1edbi t\u1eadn nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. T\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng sinh t\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u00f3 pizza ngon nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1edbi CLB l\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sarri va Koulibaly\" title=\"Sarri va Koulibaly\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/Sarri-va-Koulibaly.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Napoli nh\u01b0 Koulibaly \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00ec Sarri</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec Sarri, m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Napoli nh\u01b0 Lorenzo Insigne, Dries Mertens, Kalidou Koulibaly hay Faouzi Ghoulam\u2026 \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1edbi v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. H\u1ecd \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t Partenopei h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m g\u00ec th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 ho\u00e0ng kim v\u1edbi Diego Maradona.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Napoli t\u1eeb Rafa Benitez n\u0103m 2015, Sarri \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u201cthay da, \u0111\u1ed5i th\u1ecbt\u201d Napoli. T\u1eeb phong c\u00e1ch th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng, \u0111\u1eb7t s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh \u201cArrigo Sacchi \u0111\u1ec7 nh\u1ecb\u201d \u0111\u00e3 ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t tr\u1edf n\u00ean quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 h\u01a1n. V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n nh\u00ecn, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 Juventus.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNapoli c\u1ee7a Sarri thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 v\u1edbi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n \u0111an l\u00e1t \u1edf \u0111o\u1ea1n ng\u1eafn. C\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1eb7c trong m\u00f3n \u0103n tinh th\u1ea7n m\u00e0 \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o thi\u00ean thanh d\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng cho kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 t\u1edbi s\u00e2n San Paolo m\u1ed7i tu\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Napoli khien khan gia me dam\" title=\"Napoli khien khan gia me dam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/Napoli-khien-khan-gia-me-dam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Napoli c\u1ee7a Sarri lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebft kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 m\u00ea \u0111\u1eafm</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKi\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, Sarri t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Fabio Capello ng\u1ee3i khen l\u00e0 \u201cng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1nh th\u1ee9c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 sau nh\u1eefng n\u0103m th\u00e1ng ng\u1ee7 g\u00e0 ng\u1ee7 g\u1eadt\u201d. Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u n\u1eefa, Arrigo Sacchi g\u1ecdi h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i l\u00e0 \u201cnh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a d\u00e0n nh\u1ea1c Napoli\u201d v\u00e0 \u201cm\u1ed9t thi\u00ean t\u00e0i \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi Pep Guardiola, m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 chung tri\u1ebft l\u00fd v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi Sarri ph\u1ea3i th\u1ed1t l\u00ean r\u1eb1ng \u201cNapoli l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t t\u00f4i t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t\u201d. N\u1ebfu nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Napoli \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y Guardiola kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00e1ch s\u00e1o v\u1edbi nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t tr\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/hlv-pep-guardiola-napoli-la-clb-manh-nhat-184-170923.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/18/pep-guardiola-napoli-la-doi-bong-manh-nhat-toi-tung-doi-dau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/hlv-pep-guardiola-napoli-la-clb-manh-nhat-184-170923.html\">Pep Guardiola: \u201cNapoli l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t t\u00f4i t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u\u201d</span><br>\r\n<span>Sau khi to\u00e1t m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Italia, HLV Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Sarri ghi t\u1edbi 77 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi 29 b\u00e0n sau 38 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i Serie A m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Napoli ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng song kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 mong manh. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n n\u1eb1m \u1edf vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 g\u1ea7n 61%, x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 5 t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, ch\u1ec9 sau Man City, PSG, Bayern Munich v\u00e0 Barcelona.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Napoli th\u1eddi Sarri c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch Tiki-Taka c\u1ee7a Barca song c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n h\u01a1n. C\u00f9ng xem b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Lazio trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng vang d\u1ed9i 4-1 ngay t\u1ea1i Olimpico (th\u00e1ng 9/2017) \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng nh\u1eefng n\u00e9t \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh trong l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a Napoli v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Lazio t\u1ea1i Serie A m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/13/ban-thang-cua-Napoli-truoc-Lazio.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u Chelsea, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Roman Abramovich \u0111\u00e3 m\u00ea m\u1ea9n nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady t\u1eeb l\u00e2u. Nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i phi\u1ec7t ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 The Blues ch\u01a1i th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 v\u00e0 sau nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Guardiola, gi\u1edd h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng v\u1edbi tri\u1ebft l\u00fd t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay th\u1ebf Conte b\u1eb1ng Sarri G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay th\u1ebf Conte b\u1eb1ng Sarri G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/Chelsea-thay-conte-sarri.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chelsea m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n th\u1eddi Sarri</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec Sarri, Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng sa th\u1ea3i Conte v\u00e0 th\u00eam 6 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng v\u1edbi Napoli. T\u1ea1i CLB c\u0169, Sarri kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n l\u1ef1c. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Napoli trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi Juventus t\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u v\u00ec h\u1ecd thi\u1ebfu chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1eafp t\u1edbi, Sarri s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1eefa trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p HLV khi ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Chelsea. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 59, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 tr\u1ebb k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong ngh\u1ec1, h\u01a1n Conte tr\u00f2n 10 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng th\u00edch m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed3 th\u1ec3 thao, gh\u00e9t nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 vest thi\u1ebfu tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u1eabn c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Vi\u1ec7c Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay th\u1ebf Conte b\u1eb1ng Sarri \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"MsoTableGrid\" style=\"background:#FFFFCC;border-collapse:collapse;border:none;mso-border-alt:\n solid black .5pt;mso-border-themecolor:text1;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-padding-alt:\n 0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"1\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:0;mso-yfti-firstrow:yes\">\r\n            <td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border:solid black 1.0pt;mso-border-themecolor:\n  text1;mso-border-alt:solid black .5pt;mso-border-themecolor:text1;padding:\n  0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt\" valign=\"top\">\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\n  mso-add-space:auto\"><strong>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 HLV Sarri:</strong></p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\n  mso-add-space:auto\">\u00a0</p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\n  mso-add-space:auto\"><em>T\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7: </em>Maurizio Sarri</p>\r\n            <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\n  ms