:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1c huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Tam S\u01b0 k\u00eau g\u1ecdi h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i x\u1ed1c l\u1ea1i tinh th\u1ea7n sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 B\u1ec9.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn h\u01a1n trong th\u1ebf b\u1ecb l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh tan m\u1ed9ng c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 mang b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0, cay \u0111\u1eafng nh\u00ecn Croatia th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 t\u1ef1 m\u00e0o, tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao Tam S\u01b0 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng khi g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u1eeda thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba v\u1ed1n lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a gi\u1edd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd th\u1edd \u01a1 h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tam S\u01b0 quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tam S\u01b0 quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/nguoi-anh-khich-le-nhau-thang-tran-vo-nghia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u00e1c huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 v\u1eabn l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean kh\u00edch l\u1ec7, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 k\u00eau g\u1ecdi h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00ec t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00e0m qu\u00e0 an \u1ee7i v\u00e0 r\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i trong th\u1ebf ng\u1ea9ng cao \u0111\u1ea7u. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alan Shearer: \u201cCh\u00fang ta n\u00ean k\u1ebft th\u00fac gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t n\u1ed1t th\u0103ng b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9. \u0110\u00e2y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u World Cup n\u00ean \u0111\u1eebng n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng. H\u00e3y n\u00ean nh\u1edb th\u00eam r\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n ra sao khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ch\u00fang ta \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, v\u1eady th\u00ec tr\u1ea3 n\u1ee3 h\u1ecd \u0111i ch\u1ee9.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh quan \u0111i\u1ec3m, c\u1ef1u Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 Martin Keown cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cT\u00f4i v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n Gareth Southgate tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t cho tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u1edd l\u00e0 t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi ch\u00fang ta mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh tinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 v\u0103n h\u00f3a chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh trong \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cC\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang mong ch\u1edd th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y, trong khi Harry Kane c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Romelu Lukaku trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua Vua Ph\u00e1 L\u01b0\u1edbi, v\u1edbi Jordan Pickford l\u00e0 G\u0103ng Tay V\u00e0ng. V\u1eady th\u00ec t\u1ea1i sao l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u01a1 ch\u1ee9?\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Anh t\u1eebng thua B\u1ec9 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u, khi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c v\u1edbi \u0111a s\u1ed1 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3, Tam S\u01b0 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u knock-out kh\u00f3 nh\u1eb1n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c to\u1ea1i nguy\u1ec7n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-anh-tan-mong-cup-vang-sau-tat-ca-suc-tre-van-phai-chao-thua-kinh-nghiem-421-190998.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/sao-croatia-tuong-anh-the-nao-hoa-ra-van-vay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-anh-tan-mong-cup-vang-sau-tat-ca-suc-tre-van-phai-chao-thua-kinh-nghiem-421-190998.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh tan m\u1ed9ng c\u00fap v\u00e0ng: Sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ch\u00e0o thua kinh nghi\u1ec7m</span><br>\r\n\u201cFootball is NOT coming home!\u201d \u2013 Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mang b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 sau khi \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn trong th\u1ebf b\u1ecb Croatia l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng. Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-anh-vs-croatia-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-421-191004.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/DT-Anh-that-bai-vi-thieu-mot-cau-thu-sang-tao-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-anh-vs-croatia-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-421-191004.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh g\u00e1c l\u1ea1i gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng: B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0, v\u1eady th\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 sao?</span><br>\r\nB\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ed3i. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u1eabn s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y sau khi ti\u1ec5n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i kh\u00e1c v\u00e0 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi y\u00ean v\u1ecb \u1edf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1204","checkdouble":"191096"},{"date":"11:40 13/07","title":"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 13/7: Juventus t\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0a Marcelo v\u1ec1 l\u00e0m \"b\u1ea7u b\u1ea1n\" v\u1edbi Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/13/ngay-hom-nay-137.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (13/7). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c CLB l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</h2>(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)<br>\r\n<h2>Juventus t\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0a Marcelo v\u1ec1 l\u00e0m \"b\u1ea7u b\u1ea1n\" v\u1edbi Ronaldo\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/marcelo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\nC\u00fa \u00e1p phe l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u1ef9 m\u00e3n khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Ronaldo. Tuy nhi\u00ean, L\u00e3o b\u00e0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i. T\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u00e0 th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean TTCN n\u00e0y, Juventus mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao n\u1eefa t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ai kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n Marcelo c\u1ee7a Ronaldo. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 m\u1eadt thi\u1ebft t\u1eeb trong s\u00e2n l\u1eabn ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1eddi t\u1ea1i Bernabeu. Marcelo kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh CR7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin s\u1ebd l\u00e0m ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Marcelo \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea5n n\u00fat \"theo d\u00f5i\" t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Instagram c\u1ee7a Juventus. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3n tr\u1edf xung quanh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1edfi Real ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u00edt h\u01a1n 60 tri\u1ec7u euro. M\u00e0 ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Juventus ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n d\u01b0 d\u1ea3 sau khi d\u1ed1c ti\u1ec1n mua Ronaldo.<br>\r\n<h2>Carvalho \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn t\u1edbi La Liga</h2>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u CLB l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 William Carvalho c\u1ee7a Sporting l\u1ea1i nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi gia nh\u1eadp Real Betis. Theo AS, gi\u1eefa 2 CLB \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i chung sau cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.\r\n<h2>Fekir v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft t\u1edbi Liverpool</h2>\r\nT\u1edd Mirror cho bi\u1ebft ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nabil Fekir \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool v\u1edbi Lyon trong k\u1ef3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/chuyen-nhuong-c187-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018</span> d\u00f9 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb h\u1ee7y b\u1ecf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi VCK World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 137, tin n\u00f3ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 137, tin n\u00f3ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-137,-tin-nong-chuyen-nhuong-he-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Fekir</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Everton c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Galatasaray</h2>\r\nDo kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Everton, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Henry Onyekuru \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u1ea3ng g\u1eedi t\u1edbi Galatasaray theo b\u1ea3n H\u0110 cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Onyekuru c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Everton h\u1ed3i m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c The Toffees cho Anderlecht m\u01b0\u1ee3n.\r\n<h2>West Ham ph\u00e1 k\u1ec9 l\u1ee5c mua Anderson</h2>\r\nSkySport cho bi\u1ebft West Ham \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Felipe Anderson c\u1ee7a Lazio v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed The Hammers. D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil s\u1ebd t\u1edbi London l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1203","checkdouble":"191098"},{"date":"07:02 13/07","title":"T\u00e2n HLV Emery b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/13/tan-hlv-emery-bao-tin-buon-cho-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau 5 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, t\u00e2n HLV Arsenal tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ch\u1ed1t s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2>Arsenal s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1eddi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m, Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 SV\u0110 Emirates 5 t\u00e2n binh tr\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn (tr\u1eeb h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o). Trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t 2 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Lucas Torreira v\u00e0 Matteo Guendouzi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111em v\u1ec1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u Stephan Lichtsteiner, trung v\u1ec7 Sokratis Papastathopoulos v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Bernd Leno.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u00e2n HLV Arsenal kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111em v\u1ec1 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0o &ndash; tr\u1eeb khi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u1edbn. Emery cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 mua th\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 1 ho\u1eb7c 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1eefa. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 khi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u00e0o. Ngay l\u00fac n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd mua th\u00eam 1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u00edch cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Nh\u01b0ng v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, CLB \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ch\u1ed1t s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsenal tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ch\u1ed1t s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Arsenal-tuyen-bo-chot-so-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ch\u1ed1t s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau 5 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd \u1edf l\u1ea1i, ho\u1eb7c sang \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t v\u00e0 xem li\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea7n h\u1ecd \u1edf l\u1ea1i hay kh\u00f4ng. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Ramsey, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean quan tr\u1ecdng, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Vi\u1ec7c Ramsey ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 CLB. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. N&rsquo;Zonzi? T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, nh\u01b0ng Arsenal kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i N&rsquo;Zonzi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Arsenal tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ch\u1ed1t s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 mua ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1ebfu th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft, \u0111\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Wenger, h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean mua s\u1eafm ngay s\u00e1t deadline, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Arsenal ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0, nh\u01b0ng d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Emery &ndash; c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a CLB \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chieu-mo-torreira-tuong-lai-bat-dau-tu-hom-nay-172-188414.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/arsenal-chieu-mo-torreira-tuong-lai-bat-dau-tu-hom-nay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chieu-mo-torreira-tuong-lai-bat-dau-tu-hom-nay-172-188414.html\">Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Torreira: T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb h\u00f4m nay</span><br>\r\nGi\u1eefa l\u00fac World Cup 2018 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n, t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 \u00e2m th\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e1nh chi\u1ebfm th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, v\u00e0 Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lucas Torreira m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-so-huu-tan-binh-thu-5-172-190980.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/210541-4221396001_5807910584001_5807900029001-vs.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-so-huu-tan-binh-thu-5-172-190980.html\">N\u00d3NG: Arsenal ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 5</span><br>\r\nSau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Lucas Torreira, c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt gi\u1edd Arsenal ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa \u1edf phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Matteo Guendouzi t\u1eeb CLB...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1202","checkdouble":"191065"},{"date":"07:17 13/07","title":"Gia nh\u1eadp MLS, Rooney t\u1ed1 Everton ph\u1ee5 b\u1ea1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/gia-nhap-mls-rooney-to-everton-phu-bac.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Man United v\u00e0 \u0110T Anh \u2013 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Wayne Rooney ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Everton khi \u0111\u1ea9y anh sang M\u1ef9.\r\n</h2><h2>Rooney gia nh\u1eadp MLS<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7, G\u00e3 Shrek \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang DC United, sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o su\u1ed1t m\u00f9a h\u00e8. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Rooney th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn anh \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Everton v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u00e0 CLB th\u1eddi th\u01a1 \u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Rooney.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay sau khi n\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Merseyside b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m t\u00e2n HLV Marco Silva, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i r\u00f5 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 Rooney &ndash; \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 anh ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a CLB \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. Song song v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t \u0111i nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Rooney \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n c\u00f9ng DC United, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 cho vui r\u1eb1ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rooney ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Everton sau khi gia nh\u1eadp MLS h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Rooney ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Everton sau khi gia nh\u1eadp MLS h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/roon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rooney ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Everon sau khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi MLS</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean ESPN v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Wayne Rooney cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u1edf Man United, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i 2 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng, ch\u1eb3ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec. Tuy v\u1eady, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u00f4i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Everton.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng n\u1ebfu t\u00f4i ra \u0111i. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft l\u00fd do \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 g\u00ec. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u d\u00f9 ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. D\u00f9 sao, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi MLS&rdquo; &ndash; Rooney ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Everton.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Everton r\u1eb1ng, nghe n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ebb con. N\u1ebfu h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4i ra \u0111i, h\u00e3y n\u00f3i r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. N\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4i \u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u00ec h\u00e3y cho t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft. Sau c\u00f9ng, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp DC United v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/vua-sang-dc-united-rooney-nhan-vinh-du-lon-chua-tung-co-184-190307.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/vua-sang-dc-united-rooney-nhan-vinh-du-lon-chua-tung-co.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/vua-sang-dc-united-rooney-nhan-vinh-du-lon-chua-tung-co-184-190307.html\">V\u1eeba sang DC United, Rooney nh\u1eadn vinh d\u1ef1 l\u1edbn ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3</span><br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Man United v\u00e0 \u0110T Anh &ndash; Wayne Rooney \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean cho ng\u00e0y 2/7 h\u00e0ng n\u0103m.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-rooney-xac-nhan-ben-do-moi-172-189906.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/11/chinh-thuc-rooney-xac-nhan-ben-do-moi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-rooney-xac-nhan-ben-do-moi-172-189906.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Rooney x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Wayne Rooney gia nh\u1eadp DC United thu\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 MLS.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1201","checkdouble":"191066"},{"date":"07:32 13/07","title":"K\u1ebft th\u00fac chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup, Harry Kane tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/ket-thuc-chien-dich-world-cup-harry-kane-tran-tre-hy-vong-vao-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec1 ra, nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane tin t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0110T Anh s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2>Tam S\u01b0 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c FA giao nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, \u0110T Anh th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1ee9c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng khi n\u1eb1m trong Top 4 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, khi \u0110T Anh c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn v\u1edbi l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Kane v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 v\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Tottenham cho r\u1eb1ng, anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u cho nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, v\u00e0 \u0110T Anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, h\u01a1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft th\u00fac. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng n\u1ec1n m\u00f3ng v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc trong v\u00f2ng 2 n\u0103m qua v\u1edbi HLV, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng, \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp theo.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Kane tin t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0110T Anh sau World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Harry Kane tin t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0110T Anh sau World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/Harry-Kane-tin-tuong-tuong-lai-DT-Anh-sau-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Kane tin t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0110T Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd th\u00eam 20 n\u0103m cho m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft ti\u1ebfp theo. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. 2 n\u0103m t\u1edbi, EURO s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, t\u00f4i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o cho m\u00e0u \u00e1o n\u00e0y. Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 trong s\u1ef1 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Khi b\u1ea1n nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 n\u00e0y, l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb, v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf HLV Gareth Southgate ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi n\u1eafm \u0111\u1ed9i trong v\u00f2ng 2 n\u0103m. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o cho d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u00e1c C\u0110V r\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ra s\u00e2n m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c nghe ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 h\u00e1t vang, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111\u00e1ng kinh ng\u1ea1c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u1edf m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ed1t &ndash; m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 tr\u1ebb trung, thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ai mong \u0111\u1ee3i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;B\u00e2y gi\u1edd, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1eafc n\u1ee3 ch\u00ednh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo&rdquo; &ndash; Harry Kane tin t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0110T Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-thua-croatia-khi-chien-thang-khong-thuoc-ve-nhung-trai-tim-yeu-duoi-421-191058.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/anh-thua-croatia-khi-chien-thang-khong-thuoc-ve-nhung-trai-tim-yeu-duoi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-thua-croatia-khi-chien-thang-khong-thuoc-ve-nhung-trai-tim-yeu-duoi-421-191058.html\">Anh thua Croatia: Khi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng tr\u00e1i tim y\u1ebfu \u0111u\u1ed1i</span><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi Anh t\u1ef1 b\u1ecf \u0111i l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia. V\u00e0 ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd v\u1ee1 m\u1ed9ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-ly-do-khien-tam-su-khong-the-di-den-tran-dau-cuoi-cung-421-191024.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/4-ly-do-khien-tam-su-khong-the-di-den-tran-dau-cuoi-cung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-ly-do-khien-tam-su-khong-the-di-den-tran-dau-cuoi-cung-421-191024.html\">4 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Tam S\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qu\u00e1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Southgate t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1eabn t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc. D\u01b0\u1edbi...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/doi-vao-chung-ket-gap-phap-dt-anh-bi-mbappe-cuoi-vao-mat-421-191017.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/doi-vao-chung-ket-gap-phap-dt-anh-bi-mbappe-cuoi-vao-mat.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/doi-vao-chung-ket-gap-phap-dt-anh-bi-mbappe-cuoi-vao-mat-421-191017.html\">\u0110\u00f2i v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p, \u0110T Anh b\u1ecb Mbappe c\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Southgate g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean Croatia r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch n\u00e0y. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Kylian Mbappe c\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1ea1o \u0110T Anh v\u00ec th\u00f3i \u1ea3o...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1200","checkdouble":"191067"},{"date":"07:50 13/07","title":"V\u1eeba sang Man City, bom t\u1ea5n Mahrez \u0111\u00e3 \u201cn\u1ed5\u201d tung tr\u1eddi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/vua-sang-man-city-bom-tan-mahrez-da-no-tung-troi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>R\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gia nh\u1eadp nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Riyad Mahrez h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i Man City v\u00e0 \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn.\r\n</h2><h2>Mahrez tung Man xanh l\u00ean m\u00e2y<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 2 k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eeba qua m\u1eafc k\u1eb9t t\u1ea1i Leicester City, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Algeria \u0111\u00e3 to\u1ea1i nguy\u1ec7n khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n sang Etihad. Riyad Mahrez l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a CLB, khi gia nh\u1eadp Man City v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vui m\u1eebng khi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t, ch\u1eb3ng l\u1ea1 khi Mahrez li\u00ean t\u1ee5c d\u00e0nh cho Man City nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y cho r\u1eb1ng, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c r\u1ea5t s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Man xanh, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng &ldquo;ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e3 thua&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh n\u0103m 2016 cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Man City, sau khi th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng &ndash; b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng suy ngh\u0129, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00e0o h\u00f4m nay. \u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. <strong>Man City h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ebfc.&rdquo;<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Riyad Mahrez h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i Man City sau v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Riyad Mahrez h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i Man City sau v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/mahrez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Riyad Mahrez h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;S\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Man City, b\u1edfi b\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 11 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i (Leicester) ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i h\u1ecd, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Man City c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u00e0 ch\u1edd xem nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 tham v\u1ecdng ti\u1ebfn xa. V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t CLB \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p Champions League, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c th\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i danh hi\u1ec7u. Ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB nh\u01b0 v\u1eady&rdquo; &ndash; Riyad Mahrez h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i Man City.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bom-tan-60-trieu-bang-riyad-mahrez-cua-man-city-khung-khiep-co-nao-172-191050.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/bom-tan-60-trieu-bang-riyad-mahrez-cua-man-city-khung-khiep-co-nao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bom-tan-60-trieu-bang-riyad-mahrez-cua-man-city-khung-khiep-co-nao-172-191050.html\">&ldquo;Bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Riyad Mahrez c\u1ee7a Man City kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp c\u1ee1 n\u00e0o?</span><br>\r\nMan City mua Riyad Mahrez th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Man xanh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. V\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1199","checkdouble":"191068"},{"date":"08:15 13/07","title":"V\u1eeba t\u1edbi Juve, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i bu\u1ed3n nh\u01b0 m\u1ea5t s\u1ed5 g\u1ea1o","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/vua-toi-juve-ronaldo-da-khien-dong-doi-buon-nhu-mat-so-gao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng ki\u1ec7t xu\u1ea5t v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 t\u1ea1i Juve. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Cuadrado b\u1ecb Ronaldo l\u1ed9t \u00e1o \u2013 b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Colombia \u0111ang l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 \u00e1o n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nCuadrado mi\u1ec7ng c\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0ng l\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed5 trong tim<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ed1 7 ph\u1ea3i thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 CR7, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0 thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n c\u00e3i. V\u00e0 c\u0169ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 Javier Pastore ph\u1ea3i trao s\u1ed1 \u00e1o cho Neymar t\u1ea1i PSG, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Juan Cuadrado c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i cay \u0111\u1eafng d\u00e0nh cho Ronaldo s\u1ed1 7 y\u00eau th\u00edch, d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfng l\u00e0 <strong>&ldquo;nh\u01b0\u1eddng&rdquo;.</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i \u0111\u0103ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y tr\u00ean Instagram, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia \u0111\u00e3 &ldquo;t\u01b0\u01a1i c\u01b0\u1eddi&rdquo; c\u1ea7m chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 v\u1edbi t\u00ean Ronaldo \u0111\u1eb1ng sau, \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng t\u00e2n binh t\u1edbi Juventus.<em> &ldquo;Ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng anh trong cu\u1ed9c phi\u00eau l\u01b0u m\u1edbi n\u00e0y&rdquo; </em>&ndash; Cuadrado vi\u1ebft.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, Juventus s\u1ebd trao chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 cho Ronaldo b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 Cuadrado c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd hay kh\u00f4ng. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CLB n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u0103ng l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n c\u1ee7a n\u00e0y, c\u00f9ng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i m\u00e0 Cuadrado kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft n\u00ean vui hay bu\u1ed3n: <em>&ldquo;Qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi ch\u00e0o \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. </em><strong><em>T\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n n\u00ean trao \u0111i, thay v\u00ec nh\u1eadn l\u1ea1i.&rdquo;</em></strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cuadrado b\u1ecb Ronaldo l\u1ed9t \u00e1o Ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cuadrado b\u1ecb Ronaldo l\u1ed9t \u00e1o Ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/Cuadrado-bi-Ronaldo-lot-ao-Nguoi-trong-cuoc-noi-gi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus v\u00e0 b\u00e0i \u0111\u0103ng Cuadrado b\u1ecb Ronaldo l\u1ed9t \u00e1o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nNgay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Paulo Dybala \u0111\u00e3 &ldquo;nh\u1ea3y&rdquo; v\u00e0o troll ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 30 tu\u1ed5i:<strong> &ldquo;Th\u00f4i n\u00e0o, h\u00e3y th\u00e0nh th\u1eadt \u0111i. Anh \u0111ang r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng?&rdquo;</strong>, c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u01b0\u1eddi ra n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, &ldquo;n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n&rdquo; Cuadrado v\u1eabn b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ch\u1eb3ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn anh: <em>&ldquo;\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u00e0m theo b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng. <strong>Quan tr\u1ecdng g\u00ec </strong>m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u00e1o sau l\u01b0ng, t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i \u0111eo s\u1ed1 588.&rdquo;</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c Cuadrado b\u1ecb Ronaldo l\u1ed9t \u00e1o &ldquo;trong h\u00f2a b\u00ecnh&rdquo;, \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u l\u1ea1c quan v\u1edbi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. Ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng l\u1eddi n\u00f3i, CR7 th\u1eeba bi\u1ebft anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1eb7c quy\u1ec1n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Juve.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ronaldo-phai-toi-juventus-vi-messi-184-191064.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/11/ronaldo-phai-toi-juventus-vi-messi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ronaldo-phai-toi-juventus-vi-messi-184-191064.html\">Ronaldo ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi Juventus v\u00ec&hellip; Messi?</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man United &ndash; Ryan Giggs chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-sang-juve-quan-domino-tren-ttcn-da-do-421-191051.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/ronaldo-sang-juve-quan-domino-tren-ttcn-da-do.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-sang-juve-quan-domino-tren-ttcn-da-do-421-191051.html\">Ronaldo sang Juve: Qu\u00e2n domino tr\u00ean TTCN \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5</span><br>\r\nTh\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1198","checkdouble":"191069"}]}